        {
            "id": 6429953,
            "title": "〈台股盤中〉3萬9關前震撼教育 狂漲千點創38921點新高後翻黑",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>在地緣政治風險降溫與財報表現強勁帶動下，美股前日齊揚，台股今 (23) 日延續近期創高氣勢，在電子權值股挺身而出、AI、IC 設計族群相關題材表現下，早盤開高走高，大漲逾千點，不僅成功站回 3 萬 8 千點大關，更一度觸及歷史新天價 38,921 點，隨後大盤急轉直下，翻黑一度下跌逾 400 點，最低來到 37422 點，震幅高達約 1500 點，單日成交量預估暴增至 1.5 兆元。</p></section><p><template id=\"P:1\"></template></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股部分，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 因董事長魏哲嘉在北美技術論壇上，首度展示 A13 製程，預計 2029 年量產，激勵今早開高走高，一度再攻新高價 2,135 元，漲 85 元或 3.9%；台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 大漲逾 4%，晶元電子 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2449:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2449-TW</a>) 漲半根停版，股價一度站上 300 元。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>) 漲 6.8%、日月光投控 (3711 -TW) 漲 6%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 則受惠主動式 ETF 持續買入漲 4.7%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 早盤震盪持平，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 則下挫跌 2.5%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>為與輝達爭鋒，Google 發表第 8 代 TPU 晶片，今日台廠相關供應鏈包括富士達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6805:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6805\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6805-TW</a>)、精測 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6510:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6510-TW</a>)、旺矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6223:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6223-TW</a>)，早盤開紅上揚一度漲逾 4%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>IC 設計族群今股價依舊表現凌厲，包括創意 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2443-TW</a>)、雅特力 - KY (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6907:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6907\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6907-TW</a>)、譜瑞 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4966:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4966\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4966-TW</a>)、愛普 *(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6531:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6531\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6531-TW</a>) 一度亮燈漲停，盤中 10 時左右漲幅收斂。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光通訊股部分受惠業績亮眼，激勵聯亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>)、統新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6426:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6426\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6426-TW</a>) 一度亮燈漲停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>法人指出，台數擺脫盤整，連 3 天改寫歷史新高，技術面延續多頭趨勢，有利短線偏多表現，惟遇急漲反須提防獲利賣壓可能，盤面上受惠題材族群輪動表現，投資可依短期均線變化，順勢換股操作。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今晨收盤的美股指數部分，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊工業指數</a>上漲 340.65 點或 0.69%，收 49,490.03 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>上漲 397.6 點或 1.64%，收 24,657.57 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a> 漲 73.89 點或 1.05%，收 7,137.9 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費半</a>指數上漲 262.05 點或 2.72%，收 9,909.27 點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6429953",
