        {
            "id": 6430055,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 應廣(6716)大跌7.93%，報77.8元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>應廣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6716:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6716\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6716-TW</a>)23日10:26股價下跌6.7元，報77.8元，跌幅7.93%，成交637張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>應廣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6716:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6716\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6716-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為IC設計。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲12.97%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲9.79%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+98 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+112 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-14 張</li> <li>融資增減：+310 張</li> <li>融券增減：+7 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6430055",
